<varlistentry id="options.MyStyle">
	<term>MyStyle</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Styles for different Pager properties are called from the file "pager", and the associated MyStyle definitions are located in a selected Look file. Fonts, foreground and background colors, gradients, pixmaps, and transparencies can be specified for Pager's components.</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="MyStyle#synopsis">MyStyle definition</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
